item.title: Privacy Policy
item.description: Privacy Policy for Lokerku At Lokerku, accessible from lokerku.github.io, one of our main priorities is the privacy of our visitors. This Privacy Policy document contains types of information that is collected and recorded by Lokerku and how we use it. If you have additional questions or require more information about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us. Log Files Lokerku follows a standard procedure of using log files. These files log visitors when they visit websites.
